{"tid":2253719,"cid":5,"subCid":10,"title":"菲律賓議員憂大批中國人入境從事博弈產業、退休移民，恐釀國安風險","createTime":"2020-10-22T10:48:47.000Z","updateTime":"2020-10-22T10:52:07.000Z","uid":48083,"like":3,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":3,"replies":[{"pid":"bb4fc349f8a63951d722f5c4ae697310be595bc5","tid":2253719,"uid":48083,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-10-22T10:48:47.000Z","msg":"（中央社）菲律賓參議員漢迪夫洛斯20日說，2017年以來，約300萬名到菲國從事博弈工作的中國公民額外支付費用，以順利入境菲律賓，移民局受賄和相關人員所得可能達400億披索。<br />\n漢迪夫洛斯（Risa Hontiveros）發布新聞稿表示，根據移民局資料，2017年以來有400萬中國公民入境，數字非常驚人，比菲律賓人口最多的城市－奎松市（Quezon，約294萬居民）人口還要多。<br />\n她表示，400萬中國公民中，約380萬人沒有申請落地簽證，15萬人持落地簽入境菲律賓。<br />\n漢迪夫洛斯說，沒有申請落地簽的中國公民中，約300萬人支付額外的1萬披索（約合新台幣6000元），以順利持旅遊簽證入境菲國。這筆金額部分流向移民局官員。<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.thenewslens.com/article/142205\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.thenewslens.com%2Farticle%2F142205&d=mhl3ai6H9Odyk596tiaOPcg3oUHlS2gCMg1IFosJMKY%3D&h=c5d0f712\" target=\"_blank\">https://www.thenewslens.com/article/142205</a>"},{"pid":"2dea8f6a95cfbe971029bccd87525a84ab281c47","tid":2253719,"uid":38777,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-10-22T10:50:18.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"082f31690d59ea0dd03c1e1fc38f57e1066abb5c","tid":2253719,"uid":290314,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-10-22T10:52:07.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}]}